Package: HydroBasin
Title: Toolbox for Automated Basin Water-Balance Analysis
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Anugraha",
           family = "Das",
           email  = "anugrahadas1@gmail.com",
           role   = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for automated basin delineation and water-balance
    analysis. Includes functionality for DEM processing, watershed
    delineation with "WhiteboxTools"", and monthly run-off calculation from
    "TerraClim" climate grids.
